#include <cstdio>
#include<cmath>

#ifndef ONLINE_JUDGE
    #define gc getchar
    #define pc putchar
#else
    #define gc getchar_unlocked
    #define pc putchar_unlocked
#endif
 

inline void fr(long long int &x) {
    register int c = gc();
    x = 0;
 
    for(; (c<48 || c>57); c = gc());
 
    for(; c>47 && c<58 ; c = gc()) {
        x = x*10 + c - 48;
    }
 
}
 
inline void fp(long long int n){
 
    if (n / 10 != 0)
        fp(n / 10);
    putchar((n % 10) + '0');
 
}
 
int main()
{
	long long int n,t;
	
	fr(t);
	while(t--){
		fr(n);
		fp(sqrt(n));
		pc('\n');
	}
	
return 0;
}
